---
import BlogPost from '$lib/layouts/BlogPost.astro';

export const title = "How far back acloudyskye's world goes";
export const date = '2026-05-19';
---

<BlogPost {date} {title}>
  <p>
    <a href="https://genius.com/artists/Acloudyskye">Genius shows</a> acloudyskye's first song to be <a
      href="https://acloudyskye.bandcamp.com/track/runaway">Runaway</a
    >, dating back to October 14, 2017.
  </p>
  <p>
    The first time Enth shows up is in <a href="https://acloudyskye.bandcamp.com/track/spaces"
      >Spaces</a
    >, from December 31, 2017. Enth doesn't show up again until <a
      href="https://acloudyskye.bandcamp.com/track/parting-gift">Parting Gift</a
    > (April 15, 2018) and <a href="https://acloudyskye.bandcamp.com/track/when-there-were-others"
      >When There Were Others</a
    > (August 4, 2018), then starts consistently appearing in <a
      href="https://acloudyskye.bandcamp.com/album/a-place-where-mountains-hide-2"
      >A Place Where Mountains Hide</a
    > (April 4-July 18 2019) and onwards.
  </p>
  <p>
    As for <em>videos</em>: the first one at all is <a
      href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mCtuRp1XecU">At Rest</a
    > (February 15, 2021), and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-mItBlsXSwY"
      >FIRST ENCOUNTERS</a
    > doesn't start until March 5, 2022.
  </p>
</BlogPost>
